{"tid":734941,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 醉啜許志安成經典，韓紅又係國寶又做過官冇人敢追","createTime":"2018-07-09T05:44:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-16T22:37:13.000Z","uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f88b66de0c986bbe543587fb8af5f85ca14228e4","tid":734941,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:44:21.000Z","msg":"有才的韓紅44歲仍獨身，當年醉啜許志安轟動一時，提到感情生活，她坦言從沒拍拖：「沒有呀，一直沒有遇見自己喜歡的人，我覺得感情生活是緣份，自己沒時間拍拖，沒辦法拍拖，狗仔那麽厲害，怎樣拍拖？」<br />\n<br />\n問曾否出現追求者？韓紅說：「之前也有，但你知道像我這樣的人，你已經成名了，別人追你，你敢相信他嗎？所以很苦！他是普通人，不是圈中人，是運動員，不成，肯定不成。」"},{"pid":"c7cc4e6a5f56252fe93cc4e834044d0432f331d2","tid":734941,"uid":133529,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:57:02.000Z","msg":"講到有人要咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcSIPh6O71OMwodI_4B7knrN2rqyJmBlSLRB4sxTSGt5kpTNzmKO\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%3AANd9GcSIPh6O71OMwodI_4B7knrN2rqyJmBlSLRB4sxTSGt5kpTNzmKO&h=eb1fbb41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"850aaa033449126f37e73f36ed6785e3af0b6630","tid":734941,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T06:03:53.000Z","msg":"44歲,以為佢就嚟60"},{"pid":"2c379b696b904abe96387c8132e28244504bb2da","tid":734941,"uid":193488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"肥版蘇絲黃"},{"pid":"ce1502256c700017d9bb3654aea9f7b1084ca454","tid":734941,"uid":101110,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2c379b696b904abe96387c8132e28244504bb2da","tid":734941,"uid":193488,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"肥版蘇絲黃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T07:03:35.000Z","msg":"人哋都有金燕玲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698b6c7cf7bdd9b91dae41dd8a42e1a6954bd7df","tid":734941,"uid":44267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"